    <item>
      <title>超过 20,000 名联邦工作人员接受了马斯克的“买断”提议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/musk-buyout-offer-accepted-by-more-than-20-000-federal-workers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[超过 20,000 名雇员（约占联邦劳动力的 1%）已签署了辞职协议，以换取延期辞职，从而使纳税人继续支付他们的工资至九月底。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/musk-buyout-offer-accepted-by-more-than-20-000-federal-workers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 16:54:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将指示官员加大对伊朗的经济压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-to-direct-officials-to-ramp-up-economic-pressure-on-iran</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，唐纳德·特朗普总统将发布一项旨在加大对伊朗经济压力的指令，以履行其前任总统所作的承诺，扭转其所认为的宽松的制裁执行制度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-to-direct-officials-to-ramp-up-economic-pressure-on-iran</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 16:41:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
